================================================================================
PRO TRIAL / PRO LICENSE
================================================================================

The Pro Trial is available free of charge for 6 months per device. Use of the
Pro Trial or any paid Pro license is subject to the following additional terms:

5. DATA COLLECTION (PRO TIER)
   By activating a Pro or Trial license you consent to the collection of:
   (a) Your email address — used for license issuance, renewal notices, rule
       pack updates, and policy communications.
   (b) A device fingerprint — a one-way cryptographic hash of hardware
       identifiers used to bind the license to your device. This hash cannot
       be reversed to identify your specific hardware.

   These details are stored on VaultMorph servers located in the European Union
   (OCI Frankfurt region) and are not sold or shared with third parties.

6. DEVICE LIMITS
   The Pro Trial permits activation on up to 2 devices per email address.
   Attempting to circumvent device limits (e.g. via automated signups) may
   result in revocation of all associated licenses.

7. FAIR USE
   The Pro Trial is intended for individual use. Organisations requiring
   more than 10 concurrent users must obtain an Enterprise license.

